full_title: PAID by ¥$, Kanye West & Ty Dolla $ign
title: PAID

description.plain:
On “PAID,” track 3 off VULTURES 1, Kanye West and Ty Dolla $ign rap about getting money and their party life.

The track samples Jodeci’s 1995 track “Get On Up” and Cajmere’s 1994 track “Brighter Days (Underground Goodies Mix).”
